9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Hijack 1971 | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Based on a real event, an easy Korean domestic flight bound for Gimpo takes an ill-fated turn when one of the passengers, Yong-dae (Yeo Jin-goo), hijacks the plane with a bomb, demanding to change the flight’s path to North Korea, where his brother lives. With the captain (Sung Dong-il) losing his eyesight from the initial bomb blast, co-pilot Tae-in takes over the flight and fights to save the lives of the passengers, along with the flight attendant Ok-soon (Chae Soo-bin)."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/102565/hijack-1971"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Hijack 1971"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Based on a real event, an easy Korean domestic flight bound for Gimpo takes an ill-fated turn when one of the passengers, Yong-dae (Yeo Jin-goo), hijacks the plane with a bomb, demanding to change the flight’s path to North Korea, where his brother lives. With the captain (Sung Dong-il) losing his eyesight from the initial bomb blast, co-pilot Tae-in takes over the flight and fights to save the lives of the passengers, along with the flight attendant Ok-soon (Chae Soo-bin)."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/102565/hijack-1971"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/68jNkFi61MQjrJEqj2up5wZ4w5R.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Hijack 1971"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Based on a real event, an easy Korean domestic flight bound for Gimpo takes an ill-fated turn when one of the passengers, Yong-dae (Yeo Jin-goo), hijacks the plane with a bomb, demanding to change the flight’s path to North Korea, where his brother lives. With the captain (Sung Dong-il) losing his eyesight from the initial bomb blast, co-pilot Tae-in takes over the flight and fights to save the lives of the passengers, along with the flight attendant Ok-soon (Chae Soo-bin)."}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/68jNkFi61MQjrJEqj2up5wZ4w5R.jpg"}],["$","link","14",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.svg"}],["$","$L11","15",{}]],"error":null,"digest":"$undefined"}
